  "title": "Resident Physician (Geriatric/Rehabilitative Care)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Provide day-to-day clinical care and management for inpatients, focusing on rehabilitation, recovery, and stabilization.</li><li>Participate in multidisciplinary rounds and family case discussions to support integrated discharge planning.</li><li>Monitor chronic conditions, functional recovery, and respond to acute medical issues in a step-down setting.</li><li>Ensure documentation and compliance with institutional care standards and regulatory expectations.</li><li>Contribute to a team-based culture by guiding junior staff and supporting continual service improvement.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Medical degree (MBBS or MD) accredited by the Singapore Medical Council (SMC).</li><li>Fully registered with the SMC and eligible to practice in Singapore.</li><li>At least 3 years of post-housemanship clinical experience.</li><li>Passion for <strong>geriatric or rehabilitative care</strong>, especially in <strong>step-down or community settings.</strong></li><li>Additional training or experience in <strong>family medicine, gerontology, or palliative care is advantageous.</strong></li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
